Important correction:
The original adata.X contained log-normalized expression values.
Raw count data were found in adata.raw.X.

adata.X:
integer values: False

adata.raw.X:
integer values: True
min: 1.0
max: 8294.0

Therefore, adata.raw.X was used to construct the final reference AnnData for RegressionModel training.

Output file:
cell2location_run/processed/ref_broad_adult_downsample.h5ad

Conclusion:
Downsampled reference using raw counts was successfully prepared.
